data.description: BACK ON MARKET DUE TO THE 50 POUND WEIGHT LIMIT FOR DOGS, NEVER MADE IT TO INSECTION. Come see this beautiful 2 bed, 1.5 bath townhome now for sale in the highly desirable McKay Landing. A charming façade w/brick accents and a welcoming front porch are just the beginning! Inside you will find spacious living & dining areas featuring elegant newer LVP flooring, vaulted ceilings, a warm fireplace for those cold winter nights, and soothing palette throughout. The kitchen is comprised of wood cabinetry w/ample counter space, stainless steel appliances, and a serving window. Enjoy a good night's sleep in the primary bedroom, w/its soft carpet and lots of natural light. The large basement can be used as an entertainment center, bonus room, or simply extra storage space.  Also includes a quaint side patio where you can spend a relaxing evening with friends. Home owners get to enjoy a park, swimming pool and club house. The location is prime  being so close to shopping, restaurants, parks, trails and so much more. Don't miss out on this opportunity, schedule a private showing today.
